/gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=fa9a53a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=cb977ca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=a1891fc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"ce8e42a6c34d48eb0be2c76f43d9d4c23acf5bf9","tid":1667892,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba45290a4e791c8ca753f1e2e70fb19fe6818ac","tid":1667892,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68a1bc2813280fe577253e765963b621a1fe278","tid":1667892,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80d21228b582b557e5f899d38b31abf0fc244f80","tid":1667892,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"都係無。<br />\n佢唔係盛智文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶共狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"但可以玩區會？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"佢係香港人、只係攞唔到特區護照<br />\n之前公民黨有個鬼佬唔記得咩名都玩到區選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"司馬文"},{"pid":"2d97a61c52fa2192d7ce0df84b1620bedb9081a5","tid":1667892,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e15fa8e6cdfdf03d6a0b29f73d9a1639017f02e","tid":1667892,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba45290a4e791c8ca753f1e2e70fb19fe6818ac","tid":1667892,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68a1bc2813280fe577253e765963b621a1fe278","tid":1667892,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"但可以玩區會？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"佢係香港人、只係攞唔到特區護照<br />\n之前公民黨有個鬼佬唔記得咩名都玩到區選"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"吓<br />\n<br />\n踢波嗰班住夠七年都做咗香港人啦<img sr